com.vub.model

Class CourseEnrollmentAssociation

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vub.model.CourseEnrollmentAssociation

  • @Entity
public class CourseEnrollmentAssociation
extends java.lang.Object
    Class which represents the association between Course and User. Every Course has many users, and every user has many courses. This class maps that relationship.
